# Global UI System 
**Element**	 |  **Spec**
Grid: 12-col / 8 pt rhythm; 1440 px max; 2 rem outer gutters.
Spacing: XS 4 px · S 8 px · M 16 px · L 32 px · XL 64 px.
Corners: 12 px radius; badges keep truncated-hex shape.
Buttons: Primary = Safety Orange bg, Cream text, inset shadow; hover shifts hue +3%.
Cards: Charcoal bg → hover lifts +4 px, subtle soil-grain overlay 10% opacity.
Texture layer: Film-grain overlay on photos 12% opacity (blend = overlay).
Motion: 200 ms ease-out; parallax on hero bg only; no scroll-jacking.

